<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>커튼테일러 | 공간에 품격을 더하다</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: "Pretendard", "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif;
      color: #2b2b2b;
      background: #faf7f2;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    header {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 18px 8%;
      background: rgba(250, 247, 242, 0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      z-index: 100;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e8dfd3;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
    }

    nav a {
      margin-left: 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #333;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 160px 8% 100px;
      background: linear-gradient(rgba(30,25,20,0.45), rgba(30,25,20,0.45)),
        url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1618220179428-22790b461013?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80");
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-content {
      max-width: 720px;
    }

    .hero h2 {
      font-size: 58px;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      letter-spacing: -2px;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 21px;
      margin-bottom: 34px;
    }

    .btn-group a {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 15px 26px;
      margin-right: 10px;
      border-radius: 40px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: #c8a46a;
      color: white;
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: white;
      color: #333;
    }

    section {
      padding: 90px 8%;
    }

    .section-title {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 50px;
    }

    .section-title h3 {
      font-size: 36px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .section-title p {
      color: #777;
      font-size: 17px;
    }

    .cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 22px;
    }

    .card {
      background: white;
      padding: 34px 26px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    }

    .card h4 {
      font-size: 21px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: #4b3a25;
    }

    .about {
      background: white;
    }

    .about-wrap {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 50px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .about img {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 28px;
    }

    .about-text h3 {
      font-size: 38px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .about-text p {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .portfolio {
      background: #f3eee7;
    }

    .portfolio-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 22px;
    }

    .portfolio-grid img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 280px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 22px;
    }

    .branches {
      background: white;
    }

    .branch-box {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 24px;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    .branch {
      padding: 34px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      background: #faf7f2;
      border: 1px solid #e8dfd3;
    }

    .branch h4 {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .contact {
      text-align: center;
      background: #2f261d;
      color: white;
    }

    .contact h3 {
      font-size: 38px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .contact p {
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      color: #eee;
    }

    footer {
      padding: 28px 8%;
      background: #1f1913;
      color: #aaa;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      nav {
        display: none;
      }

      .hero h2 {
        font-size: 40px;
      }

      .cards,
      .portfolio-grid,
      .branch-box,
      .about-wrap {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      section {
        padding: 70px 6%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <header>
    <h1>커튼테일러</h1>
    <nav>
      <a href="#service">서비스</a>
      <a href="#about">브랜드</a>
      <a href="#portfolio">시공사례</a>
      <a href="#branch">지점안내</a>
      <a href="#contact">문의</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h2>공간에 품격을 더하다</h2>
      <p>
        커튼 · 블라인드 · 전동커튼 · 전동블라인드<br />
        전문가 직접 실측부터 맞춤제작, 시공, A/S까지 책임집니다.
      </p>
      <div class="btn-group">
        <a href="tel:010-4779-0401" class="btn-primary">전화 상담하기</a>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-secondary">방문견적 신청</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="service">
    <div class="section-title">
      <h3>서비스 안내</h3>
      <p>공간에 맞는 제품을 전문가가 직접 제안합니다.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="cards">
      <div class="card">
        <h4>맞춤 커튼</h4>
        <p>쉬폰, 린넨, 암막커튼까지 공간 분위기에 맞춰 제작합니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4>블라인드</h4>
        <p>콤비, 우드, 알루미늄, 롤스크린 등 다양한 제품 시공이 가능합니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4>전동 시스템</h4>
        <p>전동커튼, 전동블라인드, 리모컨 및 IoT 연동까지 상담 가능합니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4>상업공간 시공</h4>
        <p>사무실, 상가, 카페, 병원 등 공간 목적에 맞게 시공합니다.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about" id="about">
    <div class="about-wrap">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600566753190-17f0baa2a6c3?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="커튼 인테리어" />
      <div class="about-text">
        <h3>왜 커튼테일러인가요?</h3>
        <p>커튼테일러는 단순히 제품을 판매하는 곳이 아닙니다.</p>
        <p>공간의 분위기, 채광, 생활 패턴까지 고려해 가장 어울리는 커튼과 블라인드를 제안합니다.</p>
        <p>상담, 실측, 제작, 시공, 사후관리까지 책임감 있게 진행합니다.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="portfolio" id="portfolio">
    <div class="section-title">
      <h3>시공 사례</h3>
      <p>아파트, 사무실, 상가, 카페까지 다양한 공간을 완성합니다.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="portfolio-grid">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1615873968403-89e068629265?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="시공사례1" />
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600607687939-ce8a6c25118c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="시공사례2" />
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600210491369-e753d80a41f3?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="시공사례3" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="branches" id="branch">
    <div class="section-title">
      <h3>지점 안내</h3>
      <p>가까운 지점에서 상담받아보세요.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="branch-box">
      <div class="branch">
        <h4>인천 부평점</h4>
        <p>인천광역시 부평구 원길로34, 중앙프라자 201호</p>
      </div>
      <div class="branch">
        <h4>김포점</h4>
        <p>김포한강11로322, 154호</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact" id="contact">
    <h3>무료 방문견적 문의</h3>
    <p>커튼테일러가 고객님의 공간에 가장 어울리는 제품을 제안드립니다.</p>
    <div class="btn-group">
      <a href="tel:010-4779-0401" class="btn-primary">010-4779-0401</a>
      <a href="#" class="btn-secondary">카카오톡 상담</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    © Curtain Tailor. All Rights Reserved.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
